  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The royal family is trapped in an eternal slumber, cursed by their sins. You are among them, and your only escape lies in spotting anomalies and making the right choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.poster.avif?t=1739544094\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.webm?t=1739544094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.mp4?t=1739544094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>If there's an anomaly,</strong></i><br> <u><strong>turn back.</strong></u><br><i><strong>If not,</strong></i> <br><u>move forward.</u> <br><br><strong>Wrong choices reset all progress, so choose wisely.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somnus features over 30 possible anomalies, with plans to expand this number to 50 in future updates.<br><strong><br> <u>Play Time</u> <br>20-120 Minutes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The royal family is trapped in an eternal slumber, cursed by their sins. You are among them, and your only escape lies in spotting anomalies and making the right choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.poster.avif?t=1739544094\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.webm?t=1739544094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448300/extras/3a109d267af55cf346eaec914715baff.mp4?t=1739544094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>If there's an anomaly,</strong></i><br> <u><strong>turn back.</strong></u><br><i><strong>If not,</strong></i> <br><u>move forward.</u> <br><br><strong>Wrong choices reset all progress, so choose wisely.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somnus features over 30 possible anomalies, with plans to expand this number to 50 in future updates.<br><strong><br> <u>Play Time</u> <br>20-120 Minutes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
